Show fleet nodes, registered databases, and service placement, derived from the fleet root

Usage: sleet status [OPTIONS] <ROOT>

Arguments:
  <ROOT>
          Fleet root URL, e.g. s3://ops/sleet/

Options:
      --compactions
          Also read each database's compaction queue depth from `.compactions` (one read per database)

      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format

          Possible values:
          - text: Human-readable text
          - json: JSON matching the subcommand's response schema
          
          [default: text]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
